#: .\sa_book.json
msgid "High Level Commercial and Military Cryptology"
msgid_plural "High Level Commercial and Military Cryptology"
msgstr[0] "高级商业与军事密码学"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'High Level Commercial and Military Cryptology',
